<title>USA: Benton Oil authorizes share buy-back.</title>
<headline>Benton Oil authorizes share buy-back.</headline>
<dateline>CARPINTERIA, Calif. 1997-06-12</dateline>
<text>
<p>Benton Oil and Gas Co said Thursday it authorized the buy-back of up to 1,500,000 shares of its common stock.</p>
<p>Benton said it will use the stock for general corporate purposes including the re-issuance of shares for the company's employee stock option plan.</p>
<p>The company said it plans to make the purchases from time to time on the open market as conditions warrant.</p>
